 </p>


   <p class="jp"> 
       <span class="title_jp">雲の中のカタリナ島</span>
 パロスバーデス半島から、夕暮れのカタリナ島を南に望む。海は低い雲に覆われている。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><category term="Fog" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking south towards Catalina Island at sunset from the Palos Verdes Peninsula, while the ocean is covered in low lying clouds.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08352_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08352_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>